######################################################################################
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#IRMUE 14.06.12 AP/AR management: initializing of amount type PURPRITYP
#The amount type PURPRITYP is initialized with the Parameter PURPRITYP/GPURPRITYP.
#If Parameter PURPRITYP is not defined, the amount type is initialized with Ex tax.
#The X3 user can change the amount type always.
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$RAZCRE_PURPRITYP
If dim([M:BPS2]PURPRITYP)>0
 If dim(GPURPRITYP)>0
  [M:BPS2]PURPRITYP = GPURPRITYP
 Endif
If [M:BPS2]PURPRITYP=0 : [M:BPS2]PURPRITYP=1 : Endif
Endif
Return
################################################################################################
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#IRMUE 14.06.12 AP/AR management: initializing of amount type PURPRITYP
#If the amount type PURPRITYP is not defined, the amount type is initialized with Ex tax.
#The X3 user can change the amount type always.
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$RAZDUP_PURPRITYP
If dim([M:BPS2]PURPRITYP)>0 & [M:BPS2]PURPRITYP=0
 [M:BPS2]PURPRITYP=1
Endif
Return
